{"tid":28022,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"外國反色情組織進入中學校園宣傳","createTime":"2016-12-07T16:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T17:11:50.000Z","uid":35484,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"044c5727a9e5933d5ae4745b56353c152d93c1ce","tid":28022,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"外國反黃宣傳進入中學校園<br />\n<br />\n前言：本視頻來自於fight the new drug（簡稱ftnd）網站，是他們進入校園進行反黃宣傳的剪輯，可見國外已經有人深刻認識到黃毒的危害，希望國內也能進行一些反黃的教育宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTg0MjAzODAxNg==.html?from=y1.7-1.2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.youku.com%2Fv_show%2Fid_XMTg0MjAzODAxNg%3D%3D.html%3Ffrom%3Dy1.7-1.2&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e183826c\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTg0MjAzODAxNg==.html?from=y1.7-1.2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多fight the new drug 資料:<br />\n<br />\n在美國有一個叫做Fight The New Drug（簡稱FTND）的網站，翻譯成中文就是「與新毒品戰鬥」，而它所指的新毒品就是H片和色情。FTND的口號是「porn kills love」即「色情毀滅愛」。<br />\n<br />\n【Fight the new drug】美國人宣稱與黃片鬥爭到底 <br />\n<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ1Nzg5MzI4MA==.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.youku.com%2Fv_show%2Fid_XMTQ1Nzg5MzI4MA%3D%3D.html&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ee2b8ccf\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ1Nzg5MzI4MA==.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Fight the new drug】色情如何改變你的大腦 <br />\n<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ1ODEyMzUwOA==.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.youku.com%2Fv_show%2Fid_XMTQ1ODEyMzUwOA%3D%3D.html&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5f958dae\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ1ODEyMzUwOA==.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Fight the new drug】演唱會 <br />\n<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ1ODE0MjU2MA==.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.youku.com%2Fv_show%2Fid_XMTQ1ODE0MjU2MA%3D%3D.html&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4be71b92\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQ1ODE0MjU2MA==.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Fight the New Drug】宣傳PornKillsLove <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wDpNZD1pERY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwDpNZD1pERY&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4686bf24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wDpNZD1pERY</a><br />\n<br />\n【Fight The New Drug】youtube <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/FightTheNewDrug/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FFightTheNewDrug%2Ffeatured&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c758b2c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/FightTheNewDrug/featured</a>"},{"pid":"37619e2f7fb02fff408db086291e6a7b46105a1a","tid":28022,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"想入戒丁whatsapp群請ＰＭ電話比我 <br />\nＦＡＣＥＢＯＯＫ專頁：@noj1314 <br />\n香港戒丁文章 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=52\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D52&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4186ef87\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=52</a>"},{"pid":"73a40d1c85c4fc89141bbc41b9395c60e7a08586","tid":28022,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"西方觀點： <br />\n<br />\n人體內有一個「獎賞系統」，這個系統的物質基礎叫「多巴胺」(Dopamine)，由腦內分泌，可影響一個人的情緒，是一種類似腎上腺素的物質，在短時間內令人高度興奮。多巴胺帶來的興奮可以使人上癮，性行為、吸菸、酗酒甚至吸毒，都可以刺激多巴胺的分泌。從理論上來講，增加這種物質就可以讓人飄飄欲仙，但它卻會令人上癮，讓人深陷其中，難以自拔。很多人在無聊時、情緒差時、壓力大時，都很容易出現手淫的行為，因為他們急需通過手淫來增加多巴胺的分泌，從而讓自己興奮起來、快樂起來，以擺脫當時糟糕的心理狀態。雖然手淫惡習可以導致多巴胺超量分泌，並獲得隨之而來的欣快感，但是當快感消退，當多巴胺濃度回落，人就會變得異常空虛，所以在短暫的滿足過後，又是無盡的渴望，極希望再次體驗那種多巴胺爆髮式分泌的快感，多巴胺的瘋狂分泌就像一場頭腦風暴，給人帶來爽的體驗，但是請記住，風暴會帶來災難性的後果，這種爽為身心健康埋下了極大的隱患，很多人只看到短暫的爽，卻看不到由之引發的無量痛苦。"},